data.description:
If you are looking for an **Income-generating rental opportunity or a **Mother in-law suite this is your perfect opportunity!  This impeccably designed 5-bedroom, 5 1/2-bath residence offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable family living. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property is a true gem waiting for the right owner to call it home.

Step inside and be greeted by an open and airy kitchen that is bathed in natural light. The well-thought-out floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and gourmet kitchen, making it ideal for both daily living and entertaining guests.

The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's paradise, boasting top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, marble countertops, a generous island, and ample storage space. 

Retreat to the master suite, featuring a spacious bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a spa-like en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. This private oasis is perfect for unwinding after a long day.

 This newly remodeled walk out basement provides a private abode which offers an inviting and self-contained living space, ideal for your loved ones or guests seeking a home away from home. This suite is not limited to in-law accommodation; it can also serve as a income-generating rental unit. Its versatility adds significant value to your property.

This home is equipped with modern amenities, including central heating and cooling separate for each floor, a laundry room on each floor, as well as a 3-car garage. 

This home offers a maintenance free landscape, a spacious patio for al fresco dining, and mature trees providing shade and privacy.

Conveniently located close to excellent schools, parks, shopping, and dining. This home offers the perfect balance of suburban tranquility and urban convenience.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living!
